{"tid":100593,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"我發明左一個脫毒定理！！ (附公式)","createTime":"2017-01-30T07:01:24.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-30T07:21:47.000Z","uid":73953,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c23a196df7b02fc3f43f7d5cdee0abc3107b66d7","tid":100593,"uid":73953,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T07:01:24.000Z","msg":"根據小財不出，大財不入。<br />\n<br />\n首先搵個肥婆(小財)，然後中出即飛(出)，跟著有2個女人比你吸引(大財)。<br />\n<br />\n然後將2個女人(小財)，再中出即飛(出)，跟著多過2個女人就比你吸引(大財)。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n如此類推，不斷重覆。<br />\n到時每日有一百幾條女等住比你屌，屌到你悶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n公式如下y=1/(1-x)<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/upiqlo51\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fupiqlo51&h=8902ec02&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n你有中出24小時內即飛，n=1，y-&gt;無限，代表你將來有幾條女係視乎你無覆左幾次以上動作。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n否則n=0，你一開始唔搵肥婆等等其他情況n=0，咁個y=1，即係你一世都毒撚。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n條式只限青頭毒撚"},{"pid":"f4c7ea67f75f2a1c7e5dabb99ab7d9eef36c538d","tid":100593,"uid":73953,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T07:02:32.000Z","msg":"招肥婆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ffab01bc59fee7ac813191b4766843f446b0619b","tid":100593,"uid":73953,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T07:04:01.000Z","msg":"打錯係x=n"},{"pid":"bfa9ac3c1472f200ae2f414829e5b1aeb3dff9c7","tid":100593,"uid":73953,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T07:08:52.000Z","msg":"一"},{"pid":"79943d98cf19d220896874c940aee2f360b65bfc","tid":100593,"uid":22566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T07:08:54.000Z","msg":"點解你覺得有錢過你手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 憑咩<